        </div>
        <div class="nfb-progress-bar" data-ui-active="false" data-cy="work-page-header-progress-bar-container" data-ui-el="progress-bar" data-related-id="source:blackfly">
          <div class="nfb-progress-bar__bar-container">
              <div class="nfb-progress-bar__bar" data-cy="work-page-header-progress-bar" data-ui-el="progress-bar-inner" role="progressbar" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="nfb-work-page__header-description _nfb--has-clamped-text" data-ui-el="work-page-header-description" data-cy="work-page-header-description">
          This animated film about the pesky blackfly is based on the song of the same title, written and sung by Canadian folk singer Wade Hemsworth, with back-up vocals by the McGarrigle sisters. It recounts Hemsworth&#x27;s battles with this quintessential &quot;critter&quot; during a summer of surveying in Northern Ontario.
        </p>
