  <section class="nfb-work-page__section" data-gtm-section_name="details">
    
      <div id="details_anchor" class="nfb-work-page__section-title">
        <div class="nfb-work-page__section-content">
          <h2 class="_nfb-font__case--is-upper">Details</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nfb-work-page__section-content">
        <div id="tabSynopsis" class="nfb-work-page__long-description copy">
          
            <p>This animated film about the pesky blackfly is based on the song of the same title, written and sung by Canadian folk singer Wade Hemsworth, with back-up vocals by the McGarrigle sisters. It recounts Hemsworth's battles with this quintessential "critter" during a summer of surveying in Northern Ontario.</p>
            
          
        </div>
      </div>
      
      
        <div class="nfb-work-page__section-content">
          <div class="_nfb--has-bottom-horizontal-line">
            <button class="collapseBlock is-collapseBlock-open is-collapseBlock-open-default" aria-controls="taglist">
              <i class="icon-arrowhead" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              See also
            </button>
